{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/pemenang-bekraf-game-prime-awards-2018/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ini Dia Para Pemenang BEKRAF Game Prime Awards 2018!","content":"<p><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pembicara-game-prime-2018/\">BEKRAF Game Prime 2018</a> telah usai. Para <em>developer</em> game lokal sukses memamerkan game terbaik buatan mereka. Namun, siapakah yang terbaik di antara semuanya? BEKRAF Game Prime Awards 2018 merupakan bentuk apresiasi terhadap para <em>developer</em> dan <em>publisher</em> game Indonesia yang telah berjuang memajukan industri game lokal hingga harum namanya di dalam negeri maupun panggung internasional.</p>\n<p>Total 50 <em>developer</em> game berpartisipasi dalam Game Prime 2018, dan beberapa dari mereka berhasil mencatatkan namanya sebagai pemenang penghargaan Game Prime Awards 2018. Siapa saja yang berhasil meraih penghargaan Game Prime Awards 2018?</p>\n<h1>Most Innovative Gameplay: King&#8217;s Ploy</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49213\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49213\" data-attachment-id=\"49213\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemenang-bekraf-game-prime-awards-2018/attachment/01-game-prime-awards-2018/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-game-prime-awards-2018\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49213\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" alt=\"game prime awards 2018\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49213\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Prime</p></div></p>\n<p>Penghargaan Most Innovative Gameplay berhasil didapatkan game Kingâ€™s Ploy dari <em>developer</em> Mintsphere. Game <em>puzzle</em> ini mengangkat konsep permainan catur dengan petak yang lebih kecil dan rangkaian bidak catur yang berbeda-beda di setiap misinya. Tak hanya menyajikan permainan yang menarik dan unik, kamu juga bisa belajar konsep permainan catur dengan lebih menyenangkan.</p>\n<h1>Most Promising Game: Forged of Blood</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49214\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49214\" data-attachment-id=\"49214\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemenang-bekraf-game-prime-awards-2018/attachment/02-game-prime-awards-2018/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-game-prime-awards-2018\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49214\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: KAORI Nusantara\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49214\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: KAORI Nusantara</p></div></p>\n<p>Game strategi Forged of Blood karya Critical Forge berhasil meraih penghargaan Most Promising Game. Forged of Blood bisa jadi salah satu <em>breakthrough</em> untuk industri game Indonesia, karena menyajikan permainan strategi <em>turn based</em> yang solid ala XCOM, serta presentasi visual 3D yang sangat memukau.</p>\n<h1>Best Tabletop Game: Candrageni</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49215\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49215\" data-attachment-id=\"49215\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemenang-bekraf-game-prime-awards-2018/attachment/03-game-prime-awards-2018/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-game-prime-awards-2018\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49215\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Game Prime\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49215\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Prime</p></div></p>\n<p>Kompas berhasil memenangkan penghargaan Best Tabletop Game lewat <em>board game</em> mereka, Candrageni. Dalam <em>board game</em> yang bersetting di kerajaan Mataram ini, pemain harus membangun candi sekaligus berdagang dengan negara dan kerajaan lainnya.</p>\n<h1>Best Booth: Own Games</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49216\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49216\" data-attachment-id=\"49216\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemenang-bekraf-game-prime-awards-2018/attachment/04-game-prime-awards-2018/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-game-prime-awards-2018\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49216\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Game Prime\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49216\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Prime</p></div></p>\n<p>Own Games datang ke Game Prime 2018 untuk mengenalkan game terbaru mereka, Own Coffee Shop. Untuk menarik perhatian, mereka membangun kedai kopi betulan! Di sana, pengunjung bisa membeli kopi dan jajanan lainnya. Dengan konsep unik ini, Own Games berhasil memenangkan penghargaan Best Booth.</p>\n<h1>Best Publisher: Toge Productions</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49217\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49217\" data-attachment-id=\"49217\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemenang-bekraf-game-prime-awards-2018/attachment/05-game-prime-awards-2018/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-game-prime-awards-2018\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49217\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Game Prime\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49217\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Prime</p></div></p>\n<p>Meski bukan yang terbesar, Toge Productions menjadi salah satu publisher game Indonesia yang cukup <em>prolific</em> dan aktif merilis game-game keren. Tak hanya menerbitkan Ultra Space Battle Brawl di Nintendo Switch dan My Lovely Daughter di Steam, Toge Productions juga membantu <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/toge-productions-pendanaan-gamechanger-studio/\">pendanaan Game Changer Studios</a> sehingga mereka mampu merampungkan game My Lovely Daughter. Atas sumbangsihnya, tak heran Toge mampu memenangkan penghargaan Best Publisher.</p>\n<h1>Citizen Choice Award: Overgod</h1>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BQ0VUsesyJo\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br />\nSelama Game Prime 2018, pengunjung bisa memilih satu <em>booth</em> yang menurut mereka punya game terbaik. Bekerja sama dengan Mfun, penghargaan Citizen Choice Award jatuh kepada game Overgod milik studio game RedRain.</p>\n<h1>Game of the Year: Ultra Space Battle Brawl</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49136\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49136\" data-attachment-id=\"49136\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ultra-space-battle-brawl-game-indonesia-switch/attachment/01-ultra-space-battle-brawl/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ultra-space-battle-brawl.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ultra-space-battle-brawl\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ultra-space-battle-brawl-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ultra-space-battle-brawl.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49136\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ultra-space-battle-brawl.jpg\" alt=\"ultra space battle brawl\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ultra-space-battle-brawl.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-ultra-space-battle-brawl-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49136\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nintendo</p></div></p>\n<p>Penghargaan tertinggi Game Prime 2018 jatuh kepada <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ultra-space-battle-brawl-game-indonesia-switch/\">Ultra Space Battle Brawl</a> yang menjadi <em>game of the year</em>. Game produksi Mojiken Studio ini jadi salah satu <em>party game</em> paling solid karena permainannya yang sederhana, namun sangat <em>fast paced</em>. Proses pembuatan USBB jadi cerita yang sangat menarik, karena mempopulerkan Nintendo Switch sebagai salah satu konsol game yang jadi target incaran para <em>developer</em> game Indonesia.</p>\n<h1>Game Industry Icon: Hari Sungkari</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49218\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49218\" data-attachment-id=\"49218\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemenang-bekraf-game-prime-awards-2018/attachment/06-game-prime-awards-2018/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-game-prime-awards-2018\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49218\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Game Prime\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-game-prime-awards-2018.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-game-prime-awards-2018-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49218\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Prime</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Last but not least</em>, ada penghargaan Game Industry Icon yang diberikan kepada bapak Hari Sungkari. Beliau adalah deputi infrastruktur dari BEKRAF yang senantiasa mendukung para developer Indonesia dari balik layar.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Itu dia para pemenang BEKRAF Game Prime Awards 2018. Apa game jagoan kamu jadi pemenangnya? Semoga penghargaan ini bisa menjadi bentuk penyemangat bagi para <em>developer</em> game lokal untuk terus berkarya dan menciptakan game yang terbaik.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c4ddaf74-93ae-56ee-a526-8abfca6c165d"}}}